ranges.label: Inscription
Title page
Beginning as extant
Bāb Qaṭʻ al-ṭarīq
Kitāb al-Siyar
Bāb Faḍl al-jihād
Bāb mā yanbaghī lil-umarāʼ
al-Siyar al-kabīr
Bāb mā yajibu min ṭāʻat al-umarāʼ
Bāb man yajibu ʻalayhi al-jihād
Bāb al-irtidād wa-al-laḥāq
al-Siyar al-kabīr - B̄āb al-murtadd fī dār al-ḥarb wa-maʻahu waladuh
Bāb mā yūqafu min amr al-murtadd wa-mā lā yūqaf
Bāb al-murtaddīn kayfa al-ḥukm fīhim
Bāb man irtadda min al-muslimīn
Bāb asr al-ʻabd qabl al-riddah wa-baʻdahā
Bāb min al-murtaddīn wa-ghayrihim min mushrilī al-ʻarab fī dār al-ḥarb
Bāb mā tajūzu al-shahādah ʻalayhi bi-al-riddah wa-mā lā tajūz
Bāb al-murtadd yuṣību al-ḥadd wa-ghayrahu
Bāb mā yuṣaddaqu al-rajul fīhi min al-riddah
Bāb mā yuḥrizuhu al-ʻadūw min ʻubayd al-muslimīn wa-amwālihim
al-Siyar al-kabīr - Bāb mā yaẓharu ʻalayhi al-mushrikūna fa-yaḥrizūnahu
Bāb al-ʻabd al-maʼsūr yashtarīhi rajul
Bāb min al-fidāʼ fī mā yaṣluḥu wa-fī mā lā yaṣluḥ
Bāb min al-fidāʼ alladhī yarjiʻu ilá ahlih
Bāb fidāʼ al-ghaḍb wa-al-ʻāriyah wa-ghayr dhālika
Bāb shirāʼ al-ʻabd
Bāb mā lā yakūn fayʼan wa-in uḥriza fī arḍ al-ḥarb
Bāb aḥkām al-mustaʼminīn
al-Siyar al-kabīr - Bāb amān al-fāsiq
Bāb ākhar mimmā yakūn amānan aw lā yakūn amānan
Bāb al-ḥarbī yadkhulu al-ḥaram ghayr mustaʼminin
Bāb min al-amān alladhī yushakku fīh
Bāb al-khiyār fī al-amān
Bāb al-amān ʻalá ghayr mā yadkhulu huwa fīh
Bāb al-harbī yastaʼminu ilá ʻaskar al-muʼminīn
Bāb al-ḥarbī yastaʼminu ilaynā thumma ...
Bāb al-murāwaḍah ʻalá al-amān bi-al-juʻl wa-ghayrih
Bāb amān al-rasūl
Bāb al-sariyah tuʼminu ahl al-ḥiṣn thumma ...
Bāb mā yatakallamu bihi al-rajul fa-yakūn amānan aw lā yakūn
Bāb mā yakūn amānan mimman yadkhulu dār al-ḥarb
Bāb min al-rasūl wa-al-mustaʼmin idhā khīfa an yadulla ʻalá baʻḍ ʻawrāt al-muslimīn
Bāb al-ḥiṣn
Bāb ākhar mimmā yakūn amānan ʻalá sharṭ ...
Bāb man yakūnu āminan min ghayr an yuʼamminahu ahl al-islām
